git clone https://github.com/kayesh06/Image_Finder1.git
cd Image_Finder1/backend

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # on Linux/macOS
venv\Scripts\activate    # on Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt

DJANGO_SECRET_KEY=replace-me
DEBUG=1
API_HOST=http://127.0.0.1:8000

Go to chrome://extensions/ → Toggle Developer mode → Load unpacked → select extension/.

Open popup, set API_HOST in popup.js if needed (default http://127.0.0.1:8000).

